- abi-, proi-, etc. + voyelle = replace with j.

- Overlay "please wait" for big texts.

- If input accented, only check.

- Problem in case of words with 'æ': will be replaced by 'ae' in accenteur_main.js (before accentuation), and thus will give two possibilities for some words like 'ærem' (which has no more than one possible accentuation).


--------------------
En cas de modifs dans le code au niveau des diphtongues, mots à tester : aerius aerem saeculum auferas Boetius foederis saeculorum foenera eucharis eunuchus eundum aereum.

